Package com.pb.sawdust.tabledata.write

Provides classes for writing/transmitting data tables externally.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TableWriter
    The TableWriter interface provides a generic structure which can be used to write data tables to external sinks.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsciiTableWriter
    The AsciiTableWriter provides a TableWriter implementation which writes out data tables as "nicely" formatted text tables.
    CsvTableWriter
    The CsvTableWriter class provides a TableWriter implementation for writing data tables to comma-separated value (csv) files.
    DbfTableWriter
    The DbfTableWriter class provides a TableWriter implementation for writing data tables to the dBase (dbf) format.
    DelimitedTextTableWriter
    The DelimitedTextTableWriter class provides a TableWriter implementation for writing data tables to single character delimited text files.
    FileTableWriter
    The FileTableWriter class provides a TableWriter framework for writing data tables to files.
    TextTableWriter
    The TextTableWriter class provides a framework for writing data tables to text.
